&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7+ years of experience in Sales Operations, Revenue Operations, or comparable roles in a high-growth B2B SaaS environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to drive organizational change through complex, cross-functional project management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience delivering end-to-end initiatives, including intake, scoping, requirements, RACI/DACI creation, documentation, UAT, enablement, and change management&lt;/li&gt;
